com.paydiant.android.ui.service.account

Interface IProvisionAccountListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IPaymentAccountBalanceRefreshListener, IPaymentAccountManagementListener, IPaymentAccountManagementMetaDataListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaymentAccountManagementListenerAdapter

    public interface IProvisionAccountListener
extends IPaymentAccountBalanceRefreshListener
    The listener interface supporting the provision card operation events. Note: App developers are encouraged to use the ListenerAdapter implementations whenever possible as the Listener interfaces might get updated with new functionality/methods from one SDK release to the other. Therefore using a ListenerAdapter will make sure that there wont be any compilation issues due to unimplemented methods during a SDK upgrade.

    Since:
    4.1.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant
    See Also:
    PaymentAccountManagementListenerAdapter, IPaymentAccountManagementService.provisionAccount(com.paydiant.android.core.domain.provisioncard.ProvisionCard)
